Transformation.Name: Damage & Sig. Measures
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10063" AS ( SELECT /*+ inline */ "AFFECTED", "CASE_ID", "DEATHS", "GDP_US_DOLLARS", "HOMELESS", "INCOME_GROUP", "INJURED", "POPULATION", "TOTAL_DAMAGE","TOTAL_DAMAGE" / "GDP_US_DOLLARS" as "DAMAGE GDP RATIO",( "DEATHS" + "HOMELESS" + "INJURED" + "AFFECTED" ) / "POPULATION" as "SIGNIFICANCE RATIO" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

RowFilter.Name: Filter Rows
RowFilter.SQLExpression:
"N$10017" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "AFFECTED" , "CASE_ID" , "CO2_EMMISIONS_KT" , "COUNTRY_CODE" , "COUNTRY_NAME" , "DEATHS" , "DISASTER_TYPE" , "FOREST_AREA_PERC_LAND_AREA" , "FOSSIL_FUEL_PERC_ENERGY_CONS" , "GDP_US_DOLLARS" , "HOMELESS" , "INCOME_GROUP" , "INJURED" , "INT_USERS_PER_HUNDRED_PPL" , "MBL_SUBSCR_PER_HUNDRED_PPL" , "METHAN_EMISSIONS_KT" , "NITR_OX_EMISSIONS_KT" , "OCCURRENCE" , "PERCENT_AGRICULTURAL_LAND" , "PERC_TOTAL_PUB_HEALTH_EXP" , "PERC_URB_POPULATION" , "POPULATION" , "POWER_CONS_KWH_PER_CAPITA" , "TOTAL_AFFECTED" , "TOTAL_DAMAGE" , "YEAR"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} WHERE "TOTAL_DAMAGE" is not null and "TOTAL_DAMAGE" >1 and "AFFECTED" is not null and "AFFECTED" >1 and "DEATHS" is not null and "DEATHS" >1 and "HOMELESS" is not null and "HOMELESS" >1 and "INJURED" is not null and "INJURED" >1 )
RowFilter.Filter: "TOTAL_DAMAGE" is not null and "TOTAL_DAMAGE" >1 and "AFFECTED" is not null and "AFFECTED" >1 and "DEATHS" is not null and "DEATHS" >1 and "HOMELESS" is not null and "HOMELESS" >1 and "INJURED" is not null and "INJURED" >1

RowFilter.Name: High Income
RowFilter.SQLExpression:
"N$10076" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "AFFECTED" , "CASE_ID" , "DEATHS" , "GDP_US_DOLLARS" , "HOMELESS" , "INCOME_GROUP" , "INJURED" , "POPULATION" , "TOTAL_DAMAGE" , "DAMAGE GDP RATIO" , "SIGNIFICANCE RATIO"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} WHERE "INCOME_GROUP" ='High income: OECD' or "INCOME_GROUP" ='High income: nonOECD' )

RowFilter.Name: Low Income
RowFilter.SQLExpression:
"N$10077" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "AFFECTED" , "CASE_ID" , "DEATHS" , "GDP_US_DOLLARS" , "HOMELESS" , "INCOME_GROUP" , "INJURED" , "POPULATION" , "TOTAL_DAMAGE" , "DAMAGE GDP RATIO" , "SIGNIFICANCE RATIO"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} WHERE "INCOME_GROUP" = 'Low income' )

RowFilter.Name: Middle Income
RowFilter.SQLExpression:
"N$10078" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "AFFECTED" , "CASE_ID" , "DEATHS" , "GDP_US_DOLLARS" , "HOMELESS" , "INCOME_GROUP" , "INJURED" , "POPULATION" , "TOTAL_DAMAGE" , "DAMAGE GDP RATIO" , "SIGNIFICANCE RATIO"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} WHERE "INCOME_GROUP" ='Lower middle income' or "INCOME_GROUP" ='Upper middle income' )
